title: These ‘Tiny Trump’ Memes are Taking Over the Internet and They’re Amazing
text:
These ‘Tiny Trump’ Memes are Taking Over the Internet and They’re Amazing by Dana Eisenberg | 8:00   
The latest meme craze is taking pictures of President Donald Trump and making him really, really tiny. It sounds funny, and it’s actually even funnier than that. It started as a subreddi t, and now it’s taken over Twitter as well. The photos are amazing, and the Internet simply can’t get enough:
